{"tid":2134141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【傳銷群組】今增121宗確診　旺角Star Global公司11人染疫","createTime":"2020-07-31T13:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T09:10:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bb67aefbed0f21c5b04757f40ddccb776e65f976","tid":2134141,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2711886/【新冠肺炎】今增121宗確診%E3%80%80旺角Star%20Global公司11人染疫\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2711886%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%BB%8A%E5%A2%9E121%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%25E3%2580%2580%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92Star%2520Global%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B811%E4%BA%BA%E6%9F%93%E7%96%AB&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=f3094572\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2711886/【新冠肺炎】今增121宗確診%E3%80%80旺角Star%20Global公司11人染疫</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2710000/2711886/sick_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2710000%2F2711886%2Fsick_1024.jpg&h=52003c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港新冠肺炎疫情持續，連續第10日確診案例過百宗，衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君公布，截至今日（31日）凌晨零時，本港新增121宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，其中118宗屬本地感染，另有90多宗初步確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君表示，亞皆老街怡安閣一間售賣紅酒和化妝品的直銷公司Star Global，爆發辦公室感染，現再增加至6宗確診，及有至少5宗初步確診個案，共計有11宗案例。"},{"pid":"68ee5f087ecd67067e8bc8d9c632e7b36b86f177","tid":2134141,"uid":138964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"引人入關<br />\n識去深水埗特賣場<br />\n真病毒核爆"},{"pid":"d9df3d3409412b65037bf7124e2adaae09ffcb57","tid":2134141,"uid":202276,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"係咪亮碧思？"},{"pid":"21ee5225f6ceb12bcfeee0a6bd0558f33c92a77c","tid":2134141,"uid":162303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:48:14.000Z","msg":